# Server-side
<reply>
<data crlf="headers">
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: test-server/fake
Content-Type: text/html
Content-Length: 0

this is data even though Content-Length is set to zero
</data>
<datacheck crlf="headers">
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: test-server/fake
Content-Type: text/html
Content-Length: 0

</datacheck>
</reply>

